= class Gnome::FontSelection

== Object Hierarchy
* Object
  * GLib::Instantiatable
    * GLib::Object
      * Gtk::Object
        * Gtk::Widget
          * Gtk::Container
            * Gtk::Box
              * Gtk::HBox
                * Gnome::FontSelection

== Class Methods
--- Gnome::FontSelection.new
     
     * Returns: self

== Instance Methods
--- face
     
     * Returns: Gnome::FontFace

--- font
     
     * Returns: Gnome::Font

--- font=(font)
     
     * font: Gnome::Font
     * Returns: ((|font|))

--- set_font(font)
     
     * font: Gnome::Font
     * Returns: self as float

--- size
     
     * Returns: size

== Signals
--- font-set: self, font
     * self: the object which received the signal.
     * font: selected Gnome::Font.

